%div#reality-check-content
  %h1= l('Reality Check')

  %p=l('Options trading can become a real addiction, as can any other activity
  pushed to its limits. To avoid the danger of such an addiction, this website
  provides a reality-check that gives you a summary of your trades and
  accounts on a regular basis.')

  %p
    %label=l('Please specify your preferred reality-check interval (in minutes)')
    %input{:type => 'text' :interval => 1}

%div#reality-check-nav
  %span.button
    %button.button{:bcont => 1}= l('Continue Trading')
